WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.500 line:5%
[On stage]

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:28.500 line:5%
Teresa Teng (singing): The night is dark, all is still, and the moonlight is dim.

3
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:52.500 line:5%
The wind is chilly, the shadows are swaying; a meteorite traces the sky and a strange bird cries out.

4
00:00:52.500 --> 00:01:19.500 line:5%
Not even a hint of another person as I walk alone, which scares me out of my wits.

5
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:43.500 line:5%
The gift of money from a beautiful lady is so affectionate, it makes me feel both ashamed of myself and fond of her.

6
00:01:43.500 --> 00:02:24.000 line:5%
I see that the garden gate is ajar. Xuechun must be inside.
